reviewText: not the best movie, I bought it due to working at the pizza place where part of it was filmed.

The used price is too high!  This movie is still available brand new from the director, with a newly redesigned cover, right here on Amazon for $11.00!  It is a horror/slasher/comedy independent film.  Not really my cup of tea, but if you love B-movies, with blood/guts/nudity... it may be the film for you!
